    "prompt": "<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a straight horizontal wire and a square loop of wire. The square loop has a side length of 4 centimeters, and its top side is 4 centimeters below the horizontal wire. The horizontal wire carries a current of 2 amps from left to right, and the square loop of wire carries a current of 2 amps counterclockwise.\" src=\"/images/6c3de4a515c9aaf7f81f56c7e6f74476.svg\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A square loop of wire <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 centimeters\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"4 centimeters\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi>cm</mi></math></span></span> on a side carries a current of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 amps\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"2 amps\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> and is positioned <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 centimeters\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"4 centimeters\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi>cm</mi></math></span></span> from a long straight wire carrying a current of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 amps\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"2 amps\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> as shown. What is the magnitude of the magnetic force exerted on the right side of the square loop due to the magnetic field created by the long wire?&nbsp;</p>\n",
